            <span class="utterance" who="#buttonJ" start="2056.720" end="x">Unfortunately, I am waiting for a whole year here, and I have not received the permission to go to Palestine.<note n="15"><span class="note">At the time, Palestine was under the control of the British who severely restricted Jewish immigration. Like other survivors, Mr. Button had lost his home, his business, his belongings and the cultural and religious milieu into which he was born and was attempting to make a new life for himself and his family.
